star mergers and neutron star-black hole mergers\nqualitatively reproduces the observed r-process abundances in the Galaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Aug 2019 16:04:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-16"}
