ow matchings due to Glebov,\nSudakov and Szab\\'{o}, we determine $ex_2(K_{n_1, \\ldots, n_r}, K_s, kK_r)$ for\nall $n_1, \\ldots, n_r$ with $n_4\\geq r^r(k-1)k^{2r-2}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Aug 2019 14:17:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 25 Oct 2020 14:27:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 30 Oct 2020 12:38:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-04"}
